rs to cover security limits under <cite.query w-ref-type="FR" ebook-url-builder-container="COBALT" ID="codessectioncontents_40_id_I4a33e5f0192d11eba65782e394ca0815">.</cite.query><cite.query w-seq-number="00334" w-normalized-cite="49CFRS387.303" ID="If0f604802e2311ebb7c5ec7e1328e4bc" w-src-number="0306131198" w-pub-number="1000547" w-ref-type="LQ" ebook-url-builder-container="COBALT">§ 387.303(b)(1) or (b)(2)</cite.query>, a separate Department of Transportation prescribed form endorsement and Form BMC 91X certificate is required of each insurer. When insurance is provided by more than one insurer to aggregate coverage for security limits under <cite.query w-ref-type="FR" ebook-url-builder-container="COBALT" ID="codessectioncontents_41_id_I4a33e5f0192d11eba65782e394ca0815">.</cite.query><cite.query w-seq-number="00335" w-normalized-cite="49CFRS387.303" ID="If0f604812e2311ebb7c5ec7e1328e4bc" w-src-number="0306131198" w-pub-number="1000547" w-ref-type="LQ" ebook-url-builder-container="COBALT">§ 387.303(c)</cite.query> a separate Form BMC 32 endorsement and Form BMC 34 certificate of insurance is required for each insurer.</paratext> </codes.para> <codes.para> <paratext>For <cite.query w-ref-type="FR" ebook-url-builder-container="COBALT" ID="codessectioncontents_42_id_I4a33e5f0192d11eba65782e394ca0815">.</cite.query><cite.query w-seq-number="00336" w-normalized-cite="49CFRS387.303" ID="If1060a102e2311ebb7c5ec7e1328e4bc" w-src-number="0306131198" w-pub-number="1000547" w-ref-type="LQ" ebook-url-builder-container="COBALT">§ 387.303(b)(4)</cite.query>, insurer.</paratext> </codes.para> <codes.para> <head parent="codes.para"> <label.designator>(3)</label.designator> </head> <paratext>Form <cite.query w-ref-type="FR" ebook-url-builder-container="COBALT" ID="codessectioncontents_43_id_I4a33e5f0192d11eba65782e394ca0815">.</cite.query><cite.query w-seq-number="00337" w-normalized-cite="49CFRS387.303" ID="If10a9df02e2311ebb7c5ec7e1328e4bc" w-src-number="0306131198" w-pub-number